          <title>Is the fight over? Florida bill to allow guns on campus gets shot down</title>
          <description><![CDATA[TALLAHASSEE, Fla. (WFLA) — A rare rejection happened at the state capitol as a Republican-led bill was voted down by a fellow GOP lawmaker. Senate Bill 814 would have allowed concealed carry on college campuses, but it died in its first committee stop.]]></description>
